atz in La Roche-Guyon 104.jpg|120px]]||''Square in La Roche Guyon'' <br/> ''(Place \u00e0 La Roche-Guyon)''||c.1865||50 x 61||[[Alte Nationalgalerie]], Berlin [https://www.wikiart.org/en/camille-pissarro/a-square-in-la-roche-guyon]||104\n|-\n|[[File:Pissarro - donkey-ride-at-la-roche-guyon.jpg|120px]]||''Donkey Ride at La Roche Guyon'' <br/> ''(Promenade \u00e0 dos d'\u00e2ne \u00e0 La Roche-Guyon)'' ||c.1865||35 x 51.7||Private collection [https://www.wikiart.org/en/camille-pissarro/donkey-ride-at-la-roche-guyon] ||105\n|-\n|[[File:Camille Pissarro - Bords de la Marne en Hiver.jpg|120px]]||''Banks of the Marne in Winter'' <br/> ''(Bords de la Marne en hiver)''||1866||91.8 x 150||[[Art Institute of Chicago]] [https://www.artic.edu/artworks/6005/the-banks-of-the-marne-in-winter]||107\n|-\n|}\n\n==1866\u20131868 (Pontoise)==\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\" style=\"margin-left:0.5em; text-align:left\"\n!  Image !! Name !! Year !!H x W (cm)!! Current Location !! Cat No\n|-\n|[[File:Pissarro - pere-gallien-s-house-at-pontoise-1866.jpg|120px]]||''Pere Gallien's House at Pontoise'' <br/> ''(La maison de p\u00e8re Gallien, Pontoise)''||1866||40.3 x 55.2||[[Ipswich Museum]], UK [https://www.wikiart.org/en/camille-pissarro/pere-gallien-s-house-at-pontoise-1866]||111\n|-\n||[[File:Camille Pissarro - Still Life - Google Art Project.jpg|120px]]||''Still Life with Wine Carafe'' <br/> ''(Nature morte \u00e0 la carafe du vin)''||1867||81 x 99.6||[[Toledo Museum of Art]], Ohio [http://emuseum.toledomuseum.org/objects/55333/still-life]||114\n|-\n|[[File:Camille Pissarro - Le Gardin de Mauboisson, Pontoise.jpg|120px]]||''Le Jardin de Maubuisson''||c.1867||81.5 x 100||[[National Gallery of Prague]] [https://www.wikiart.org/en/camille-pissarro/the-gardens-of-l-hermitage-pontoise]||115\n|-\n|[[File:Jalais Hill, Pontoise.jpg|120px]]||''C\u00f4te des Jalais, Pontoise''||1867||87 x 114.9||[[Metropolitan Museum of Art]], New York [https://www.metmuseum.org/art/collection/search/437299]||116