iart.org/en/camille-pissarro/landscape-with-small-stream-1872] || 271\n|-\n|[[File:The Artist's Daughter by Camille Pissarro 1872.jpeg|120px]]||''Jeanne Pissarro, called Mimette, with a Bouquet''||1872||72.5 x 59.7||[[Yale University Art Gallery]], New Haven, Connecticut [https://artgallery.yale.edu/collections/objects/26339] ||281\n|-\n|[[File:Pissarro - The Road to Osny at Pontoise, Hoar Frost, 1873.jpg|120px]]||''The Road to Osny at Pontoise, Hoar Frost'' <br/> ''(Route d'Osny \u00e0 Pontoise, gel\u00e9e blanche)''||1873||50.5 x 65||[[Foundation E.G. B\u00fchrle]], Zurich [https://www.buehrle.ch/en/collection/artwork/detail/the-road-to-osny-at-pontoise-hoar-frost/] ||287\n|-\n|||''Factory on the Banks of the Oise, Saint-Ouen-l'Aum\u00f4ne'' <br/> ''(Usine au bord de l'Oise, Saint-Ouen-l'Aum\u00f4ne''||1873||45.3 x 55||[[Clark Art Institute]], Williamstown, Massachusetts [https://www.clarkart.edu/Collection/4486]||300\n|-\n|[[File:Pissarro - Peasant Woman Carding Wool, 1875.jpg|120px]]||''Peasant Woman Carding Wool'' <br/> ''(Paysanne d\u00e9m\u00e8lant de la laine)''||1875||56 x 47||[[Foundation E.G. B\u00fchrle]], Zurich [https://www.buehrle.ch/en/collection/artwork/detail/peasant-woman-carding-wool/] ||420\n|-\n|[[File:Camille Pissarro Barges at Pontoise The Metropolitan Museum of Art.jpg|120px]]||''Barges at Pontoise'' <br/> ''(P\u00e9niches \u00e0 Pontoise)''||1876||46 x 54.9||[[Metropolitan Museum of Art]], New York||460\n\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Camille Pissarro|state=expanded}}\n{{Lists of paintings}}\n\n[[Category:Lists of paintings|Pissarro, Camille]]\n[[Category:Paintings by Camille Pissarro| ]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|List of paintings by Camille Pissarro}}\nThis is an incomplete work-in-progress '''list of the paintings''' by the Danish-French [[Impressionist]] artist '''[[Camille Pissarro]]''' (1830\u20131903).\n\nThe catalog numbers of the listed works are as given in the Catalogue Raisonn\u00e9 of the Wildenstein Institute.<ref> {{cite book|title=Pissarro - General Catalogue of Paintings|first=Joachim|last=Pissarro|volume=volume II|publisher=Wildenstein Institute}} </ref>\n\n==1852\u20131856 (St Thomas, West Indies)==\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\" style=\"margin-left:0.5em; text-align:left\"\n!  Image !! Name !! Year !!H x W (cm)!! Current Location !! Cat No\n|-\n|[[File:Camille Pissarro - Sc\u00e8ne villageoise (1854-55).jpg|120px]]||''Landscape with House in the Woods in Saint Thomas, Antilles'' <br/> ''(Sc\u00e8ne villageoise)'' ||c.1854\u201355||23.5 x 30.5||Private collection [https://www.wikiart.org/en/camille-pissarro/landscape-with-house-in-the-woods-in-saint-thomas-antilles]||8\n|-\n|[[File:Camille Pissarro - Village au pied d'une.jpg|120px]]||''Village at the Foot of a Hill in Saint Thomas, Antilles'' <br/> ''(Village au pied d'une colline)''||c.1854\u201355||24 x 30.4||Private collection [https://www.wikiart.org/en/camille-pissarro/village-at-the-foot-of-a-hill-in-saint-thomas-antilles]||9\n|-\n|[[File:Pissarro - mountain-landscape-at-saint-thomas-antilles-unfinished.jpg|120px]]||''Mountain Landscape at Saint Thomas, Antilles'' (unfinished) <br/> ''(Village de Montagne)'' ||c.1854\u201355||26.2 x 23.5||Private collection [https://www.wikiart.org/en/camille-pissarro/mountain-landscape-at-saint-thomas-antilles-unfinished]||10\n|-\n|[[File:Pissarro - woman-carrying-a-pitcher-on-her-head.jpg|120px]]||''Woman Carrying a Pitcher on Her Head'' <br/> ''(Femme Noire portant une cruche sur la t\u00eate)''||1854\u201355||33 x 24||Private collection [https://www.wikiart.org/en/camille-pissarro/woman-carrying-a-pitcher-on-her-head]||15\n|-\n|[[File:Crique avec palmiers (Camille Pissarro) NGA 1985.64.29.jpg|120px]]||''Creek with Palm Trees'' <br/> ''(Crique avec palmiers)''||1856||24.5 x 32.2||[[National Gallery of Art]], Washington D.C. [https://www.nga.gov/collection/art-object-page.66427.html]||16\n|-\n|[[File:Camille Pissarro - Personnages discutant au bord d'un chemin (1856).