mitage at Pontoise''||1867||91 x 150.5||[[Wallraf-Richartz Museum]], Cologne [https://www.kulturelles-erbe-koeln.de/documents/obj/05010753]||119\n|-\n|[[File:Pissarro L'Hermitage \u00e0 Pontoise,1867.jpg|120px]]||''L'Hermitage at Pontoise'' <br/> ''(Vue de l'Hermitage, C\u00f4te de Gratte-Coqs, Pontoise)''||c.1867||70 x 100||[[Solomon R. Guggenheim Museum]], New York City [https://www.guggenheim.org/artwork/3465]||120\n|-\n|[[File:Camille Pissarro Vue de Pontoise Quai du Pothuis.jpg|120px]]||''Quai de Pothuis, Pontoise''||1868||52 x 81||[[Kunsthalle Mannheim]] [http://sammlung-online.kuma.art/node/2919]||123\n|-\n|[[File:Pissarro - the-banks-of-the-oise-at-pontoise-1870.jpg|120px]]||''The Banks of the Oise at Pontoise'' <br/> ''(Bords de l'Oise \u00e0 Pontoise)''||1868||54 x 65||Private collection [https://www.wikiart.org/en/camille-pissarro/the-banks-of-the-oise-at-pontoise-1870]||124\n|-\n|[[File:Camille Pissarro - Pommiers Pontoise (La maison du p\u00e8re Gallien).jpg|120px]]||''Apple Trees at Pontoise, the House of P\u00e8re Gallien '' <br/> ''(Pommiers \u00e0 Pontoise, la maison du P\u00e8re Gallien)''||1868||38.3 x 46.4||Private collection [https://www.wikiart.org/en/camille-pissarro/apple-trees-at-pontoise-1868]||128\n|-\n|[[File:Pissarro - the-lock-at-pontoise.jpg|120px]]||''The Weir at Pontoise'' <br/> ''(Le D\u00e9versoir \u00e0 Pontoise)''||c.1868||58.5 x 72||Private collection [https://www.wikiart.org/en/camille-pissarro/the-lock-at-pontoise]||129\n|}\n\n==1869\u20131871 (Louveciennes)==\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\" style=\"margin-left:0.5em; text-align:left\"\n!  Image !! Name !! Year !!H x W (cm)!! Current Location !! Cat No\n|-\n|[[File:Camille pissarro le village a travers les arbres.jpg|120px]]||''A Village through the Trees'' <br/> ''(Le village \u00e0 travers les arbres)''||c.1869||54 x 44.5||Private collection [https://www.wikiart.org/en/camille-pissarro/a-village-through-the-trees]||134\n|-\n|[[File:Road to Versailles at Louveciennes 1869 Ca