-1870.jpg|120px]]||''St Stephen's Church, Dulwich''||1870||42.6 x 52.8||Private collection [https://www.wikiart.org/en/camille-pissarro/st-stephen-s-church-lower-norwood-1870]||181\n|-\n|[[File:Camille Pissarro - Le Crystal Palace, Londres.jpg|120px]]||''Crystal Palace viewed from Fox Hill, Upper Norwood''||1871||47 x 73.2||[[Art Institute of Chicago]] [https://www.artic.edu/artworks/110541/the-crystal-palace]||183\n|-\n|[[File:Camille Pissarro - Le Crystal Palace, Upper Norwood.jpg|120px]]||''Crystal Palace, Upper Norwood''||c.1871||40 x 50.8||Private collection [https://www.wikiart.org/en/camille-pissarro/upper-norwood-chrystal-palace-london-1870]||184\n|-\n|[[File:Pissarro - all-saints-church-upper-norwood-1871.jpg|120px]]||''All Saints' Church, Beulah Hill, Snow''||1871||46 x 55||Private collection [https://www.wikiart.org/en/camille-pissarro/all-saints-church-upper-norwood-1871]||186\n|-\n|[[File:Snowy Landscape at South Norwood.jpg|120px]]||''Snowy Landscape at South Norwood'' <br/> ''Paysage sous la neige \u00e0 South Norwood''||1871||44.5 x 55.5||[[Los Angeles County Museum of Art]] [https://collections.lacma.org/node/2109784]||187\n|-\n|[[File:Camille Pissarro - The Avenue, Sydenham (1871).jpg|120px]]||''The Avenue, Sydenham''||1871||48 x 73||[[National Gallery]], London [https://www.nationalgallery.org.uk/paintings/camille-pissarro-the-avenue-sydenham]||188\n|-\n|[[File:Pissarro lordship.jpg|120px]]||''Lordship Lane Station, East Dulwich''||1871||44.5 x 72.5||[[Courtauld Institute Galleries]], London [http://www.artandarchitecture.org.uk/images/gallery/6963dcce.html]||189\n|-\n|[[File:Camille Pissarro - Near Sydenham Hill - Google Art Project.jpg|120px]]||''View of Alleyn Park, West Dulwich'' ||1871||43.5 x 53.5||[[Kimbell Art Museum]], Fort Worth, Texas [https://www.kimbellart.org/collection/ap-197121]||190\n|-\n|[[File:Bemberg Fondation Toulouse - Dulwich College, Londres (1871) - Camille Pissarro Inv.2149.jpg|120px]]||''Dulwich College''||1871||50 x 61|